\f1\fs34 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf11 If your macOS app can use a custom document type, you can create a document icon to represent it. Traditionally, a document icon looks like a piece of paper with its top-right corner folded down. This distinctive appearance helps people distinguish documents from apps and other content, even when icon sizes are small.\
If you don\'92t supply a document icon for a file type you support, macOS creates one for you by compositing your app icon and the file\'92s extension onto the canvas. For example, Preview uses a system-generated document icon to represent JPG files.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 {{\NeXTGraphic doc-icon-generated@2x.png \width6400 \height6400 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}¬}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 \
In some cases, it can make sense to create a set of document icons to represent a range of file types your app handles. For example, Xcode uses custom document icons to help people distinguish projects, AR objects, and Swift code files.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 {{\NeXTGraphic doc-icon-custom-1@2x.png \width6400 \height6400 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}¬}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 {{\NeXTGraphic doc-icon-custom-2@2x.png \width6400 \height6400 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}¬}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 {{\NeXTGraphic doc-icon-custom-3@2x.png \width6400 \height6400 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}¬}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 \
To create a custom document icon, you can supply any combination of background fill, center image, and text. The system layers, positions, and masks these elements as needed and composites them onto the familiar folded-corner icon shape.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 {{\NeXTGraphic doc-icon-parts-background-fill@2x.png \width6400 \height6400 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}¬}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf11 \
