\fs34 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf11 Use font sizes that most people can read easily.
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539  People need to be able to read your content at various viewing distances and under a variety of conditions. Follow the recommended default and minimum text sizes for each platform \'97 for both custom and system fonts \'97\'a0to ensure your text is legible on all devices. Keep in mind that font weight can also impact how easy text is to read. If you use a custom font with a thin weight, aim for larger than the recommended sizes to increase legibility.\

