\f0\b\fs34 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf11 Test legibility in different contexts.
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539  For example, you need to test game text for legibility on each platform on which your game runs. If testing shows that some of your text is difficult to read, consider using a larger type size, increasing contrast by modifying the text or background colors, or using typefaces designed for optimized legibility, like the system fonts.\
