\f0\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf11 Consider contrast and visual separation when choosing a material to combine with blur and vibrancy effects.
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539  For example, consider that:\
