\f2\b \cf2 \cb3 Prefer system-provided symbols without borders.
\f1\b0 \'a0System-provided symbols are familiar, automatically receive appropriate coloring and vibrancy, and respond consistently to user interactions. Borders (like outlined circle symbols) aren\'92t necessary because the section provides a visible container, and the system defines hover and selection state appearances automatically. For guidance, see\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://developer.apple.com/design/human-interface-guidelines/sf-symbols"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \cb3 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 SF Symbols}}.\cb1 \
