\f1\b0 .prominent
\f2\b \'a0style for key actions such as Done or Submit.
\f1\b0 \'a0This separates and tints the action so there\'92s a clear focal point. Only specify one primary action, and put it on the trailing side of the toolbar.\cb1 \
